Nick Kroll burst onto the scene in a cable sitcom (“The League” on FXX&#39;s gleefully lascivious fantasy football theme) and now has his own sketch show on Comedy Central.
Jenny Slate has been on Saturday Night Live and cast in Parks and Recreation, but is best known for her viral &quot;Marcel the Shell with Shoes On&quot; video series.
